secondary_outcome.description:
To verify the identified susceptibility genes and biomarkers in the existing COPD cohort, and then expand to be verified outside the cohort, to verify 5-7 related susceptibility genes and biomarkers;
To further explore the pathogenesis of COPD by conducting preliminary mechanism studies on the discovered susceptibility genes and biomarkers combined with big data analysis;
To build a unified copd data collection and sharing platform between local hospitals to achieve real-time monitoring of statistical analysis.
